SBCSQuarantineRecordXML.name: Trojan.Win32.Generic!BT
SBCSQuarantineRecordXML.desc: Trojan is a general term for malicious software that is installed under false or deceptive pretenses or is installed without the user's full knowledge and consent. Most Trojans exhibit some form of malicious, hostile, or harmful functionality or behavior.
SBCSQuarantineRecordXML.threatAdviceDetails: This is a high risk and should be removed immediately as it may compromise your privacy and security, make dangerous changes to your computer's settings without your knowledge and consent, or severely degrade your computer's performance and stability.
